      <div id="spiral-div">
        <h2>Spiral Drawing Test</h2>
        How this test works<br><br>
        <b>Requirements: </b>pen/pencil, paper<br>
        <b>Directions: </b> Using your writing tool, draw a spiral on your paper. Then take a picture of your drawing and upload it to predict your likelihood of having Parkinson's disease.
        <br><br>
        <div style="display: flex">
          <label>
            <div id="spiral-upload-btn">
            <input id="student-file" hidden type="file" onchange="saveFile(this, 'student')"/>
